"Beautiful Day" is the fourth album of the german duo Jazzamor (Bettina Mischke & Roland Grosch). From their first album on they had their own sound - and they kept working on it and developing it. The music of Jazzamor contains elements of different styles - jazz, lounge and pop.

"Jazz: Yes or Not?" is the question on their homepage. For their debut album "Lazy Sunday Afternoon" the answer could maybe have been "yes". But for "Beautiful Day"?
No, not really. Jazzamor is easy listening in the best meaning of this word: catchy melodies, nice vocals and refreshing music.
